{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, they put me in-- in cell 4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the isolated cell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, the very next morning I-- I found out there were other-- two Canadians and one British in one-- in one mission.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the commander was a-- a British captain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but the other two were-- were my-- my personal friends and comrades right from-- from Canada.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of them, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, he was-- once he was a-- a general secretary of [INAUDIBLE] organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were in cell 1, and I was in-- in cell 4.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then all-- all around me, the next cell was a-- was a woman's cell, where they-- where I had to go through where-- where they-- they tortured and-- and raped.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so, some Russian girls who-- who were radio operators, a couple days later, when they brought in a young Jewish woman-- and [INAUDIBLE], it is horrible, horrible stories.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you-- you-- you heard it all, you see, all this torturing, and-- and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the-- in the prison something-- something unusual-- unusual happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was a-- was a [INAUDIBLE] thing that-- at one night-- at one day, when I was-- I was up for interrogation, which was on first floor, the-- the interrogation room-- and also, the severe interrogation room, especially when they-- when they really tortured.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In this interrogation room, they just slapped you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the-- in the other room, when there-- there was-- they finally broke the spine, the Gestapo, because they were there in the same-- same prison.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, in the afternoon-- it was the one only afternoon when they interrogated me in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Usually, it was always in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found a guy in-- in my-- in my cell.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
